<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

<section class="set">
  <div class="container py-5">
    <div class="blog col-6 col-sm-6 col-md-8 col-lg-8 rounded px-3">
        
      <article class="blog-post">
        <h1 class="mb-1 mt-3">Welcome to Music Bloggers!</h1>
        <p class="blog-post-meta">By Lilia M.</a></p>
        <hr>
        <p>Here you can create blog posts dedicated to your favorite bands,
          groups, artists, etc! Music is
          something that I'm personally attached to, as it has gotten me through
          a couple of tough moments in my life. There is no pressure to only write
          about positive moments and we encourage you to express yourself in a way that
          makes you comfortable. However, please refrain from making malicious comments
          towards another person, artists included.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="blog row col-6 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4 col-xl-4 rounded">
      <div style="top: 2rem;">
        <div class="inset p-4 mb-3 rounded">
          <h4 class="fst-italic">If you would like to expand your genres/interests, please click here to get a random artist to look into:</h4>
          <% if (locals.artist) { %>
            <p>
            <%= artist %>
            </p>
          <% } %>
          <form action="/submit" method="POST">
            <button class="rounded" type="submit" class="mt-3 mx-3">Artist</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>    
    </div>
  </div>

</section>
<%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>